data.description: BACK ON MARKET! Buyer Financing Failed. OPEN HOUSE - Sat 1/6 11am -3pm.  Don't miss the opportunity to own this stunner! Designed with modern luxury and attention to detail this home is ready for new owners.  Nestled on a quiet street, this updated sanctuary shines with modern elegance, luxury, and unparalleled functionality. Benefit from the sustainable touch of solar panels, ensuring low utility bills (less than $15/mo) and eco-conscious living. Vaulted ceilings add to an open layout, highlighting meticulous finish work and seamlessly connecting the home's multiple gathering spaces. A beautifully updated kitchen boasts granite countertops, farmhouse sink, large pantry, and breakfast bar. The inviting great room offers a central point of connection for gatherings large or small. The ample daylight basement boasts a large family room, beautiful wet bar with island and eating nook, 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and a dedicated theater room with a 120" screen and projector (both included). A bonus room provides a balcony sitting area overlooking the great room as well as a large flex room. Further luxuries include a spacious 3-car garage, two laundry areas, central vac, plantation shutters, abundant storage, and a whole-home intercom system. Outdoors, the low-maintenance yard ensures weekends are for leisure, complemented by a covered deck and hot tub for relaxation. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
